org.cougaar.planning.ldm.plan
Class ContextOfUIDs

java.lang.Object
  java.util.AbstractCollection
      org.cougaar.planning.ldm.plan.ContextOfUIDs
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable, java.util.Collection, Context
public class ContextOfUIDs
extends java.util.AbstractCollection
implements Context, java.util.Collection

ContextOfUIDs is an implementation of Context. It is simply a collection of UIDs. It can be used when the "problem" or "problems" that a task is related to can be be referenced by the "problem's" UID.

See Also:
UID, Context, Serialized Form
